title: Bugg?

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: I have two clubs but neither work at all, I have see the tag and everything. Why doesn't this show in game or in lobbies. Rito pls respond :D

replies.body: Do you still have at least 5 members in them? I don't know if going below the minimum of 5 to create a tag will disable it, but this is a good chance to find out.
